</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_29" id="14r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_29_r1l2"><expan>Lıenhart<ex>en</ex></expan> Grafen cʒu Kaſtel / </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_29_r1l3"><expan>Gnedıg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> / Vns hat fürbracht / frau Kathreÿ <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Erking<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_29_r1l4">Cʒollners ſeligen vvitbe vnſer <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex>in</expan> / vvie Hans Dolman </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_29_r1l5">Jr Schefferknecht cʒü Geyſelwinden / gevangen vnd gen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_29_r1l6">Kaſtel gefüret vvorden ſeÿ / vnd 
<del rend="strikethrough">habe man v main Jn cʒü </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_29_r1l7">
<del rend="strikethrough">berechten / vnd beſchuldig Jn </del> main Jn cʒu berechten . darvmb </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_29_r1l8">daʒ er heyd angecʒundet <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> als m </del> ſülle / als man Jn be - </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_29_r1l9">ſchuldig / des er doch vnſchuldig ſeÿ / . <expan>Dar<ex>vmb</ex></expan> <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_29_r1l10"><expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> dienſt vvıllen <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> ſchıcken wöllet / daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_29_line_1576489963611_7034">man ſich an <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> armen nicht <expan>v<ex>er</ex>gehe</expan> / vnd Jn frıſten wöllet / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_29_r1l13">Alſlang / biʒ man ſich darvmb <expan>eigentlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ervare / vnd hoffet </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_29_r1l16">die <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex>in</expan> / daʒ Jr vvol <expan>ervare<ex>n</ex></expan> ſüllet / daʒ er </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_29_r1l18">vnſchuldig ſeÿ / vnd tüt <expan>daryn<ex>n</ex>e</expan> / Als etc . / Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc </ab>
