</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_29" id="14r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Lienhart<ex>en</ex></expan>, grafen czu Kastel </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>, uns hat fürbracht frau Kathrey,
              <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Erking<ex>er</ex></expan> Czollners, seligen, witbe, unser
              <expan>burg<ex>er</ex>in</expan>, wie Hans Dolman, ir schefferknecht, czü
            Geyselwinden gevangen und gen Kastel gefüret worden sey, und main in czu berechten
            darumb, daz er heyd angeczundet <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> sülle, als man in
            beschuldig, des er doch unschuldig sey. <expan>Dar<ex>umb</ex></expan>
<expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> dienst willen <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> schicken wöllet, daz man sich an
              <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> armen nicht <expan>v<ex>er</ex>gehe</expan> und in fristen
            wöllet alslang, biz man sich darumb <expan>eigentlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ervare; und
            hoffet die <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>in</expan>, daz ir wol <expan>ervare<ex>n</ex></expan> süllet, daz
            er unschuldig sey, und tüt <expan>daryn<ex>n</ex>e</expan>, als etc. Das
                <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. <expan>Antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>.
                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iii <expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan>
<expan>Michael<ex>is</ex></expan> anno ix<hi rend="sup">no</hi>.</ab>
</div>
